{"tid":1672790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反駁藍絲的論點資料庫","createTime":"2019-10-24T10:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T04:56:57.000Z","uid":71237,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"0d249bd810d2f97ad54083125413c9b785c723b0","tid":1672790,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:00:42.000Z","msg":"大家每日可能都會花唔少時間去同藍絲辯論。<br />\n其實藍絲的言論嚟嚟去去都係嗰啲，如果我地能夠建立一個資料庫，儲起可以用嚟反駁的論點，就可以節省到好多時間。<br />\n<br />\n8月初的時候我曾經用Google Sheet去建立資料庫，但由於介面唔方便、工作量龐大，所以最後不了了之。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1419849/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1419849/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n靠我一個人的力量唔可能成功，所以我決定改變方式，讓更多人可以合力完成。<br />\n所以我建立咗一個維基，等大家都可以參與。目前只係得個殼，暫時沒有太多內容，希望大家可以合力添加。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為非註冊用戶編輯維基會顯示IP address。為咗保護大家的私隱，我暫時set咗只有註冊用戶才可以編輯。"},{"pid":"afb82491e46651d8b02df18a4161662d3e77eb05","tid":1672790,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e0f0d3bd6628af15772beb94d0f0219d82c46f","tid":1672790,"uid":50218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e91ce87cb5d05016ce92904b7450ef5567307b","tid":1672790,"uid":64449,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:02:00.000Z","msg":"有得諗 整個chatbot 出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0071dc6a51daaf09e78b6a05d2c7795bf2e6abe","tid":1672790,"uid":61604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:02:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e26408846f3866cb63c0db97a2d0abd0679e8a4b","tid":1672790,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:03:19.000Z","msg":"而家個維基暫時無咩內容，需要大家參與。<br />\n如果你嫌麻煩唔想註冊account，你都可以直接喺依個post放低藍絲的論述 + 反駁。<br />\n有一定質素嘅我會幫你搬去資料庫。"},{"pid":"612488ff0e8648290942bfdcafcce180e6ccb791","tid":1672790,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:10:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"acdc171041961e051eff10ad30b8f1392cbe9a49","tid":1672790,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817c550e1e911bc96f7bee22e677c50e7a55ca92","tid":1672790,"uid":114802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"LM + pish"},{"pid":"2c8053def82a24075feed7759629d017edab2b9f","tid":1672790,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a0729ae0f8e01f207bef76e7f9a03541b0d960","tid":1672790,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:42:10.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"4bfe71b1308473368f9b55c3e3e1a1c143c7af2f","tid":1672790,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T11:07:50.000Z","msg":"如果你喺FB見到有精警的反駁，不妨save低佢比其他人都睇到。"},{"pid":"e53b3ccffe02020e69bc5d3d0992e3b36d7b2922","tid":1672790,"uid":41771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854455b6bb049d6915ab0ace56b0660196ee5a30","tid":1672790,"uid":19664,"lik